{"tid":2205285,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［Jerry你食屎啦］和你報重要聲明","createTime":"2020-09-16T16:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T18:55:45.000Z","uid":16135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f35f63518ed43784c8006f15f3c554980330a01","tid":2205285,"uid":16135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:48:27.000Z","msg":"[WhatsNews和你報重要聲明]<br />\n<br />\n新聞機構， 不可以是一盤生意。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsNews和你報（以下簡稱WhatsNews），當初是由WhatsCar和你車（以下簡稱WhatsCar）內一班志同道合的朋友自發而成。然而WhatsCar內部一些言論，令人不禁質疑言論自由受限。<br />\n<br />\n守護言論自由，捍衛真理的媒體又豈可從屬於被質疑為「一言堂」的組織？有見及此，WhatsNews一眾核心人員與WhatsNews專頁擁有人兼WhatsCar持份者Jerry Lo多次洽商，表示不能對其言行視若無睹，希望Jerry Lo能轉交其WhatsNews專頁擁有人身份以便WhatsNews日後能作為一個捍衛言論自由的媒體獨立運作。<br />\n<br />\n在Jerry Lo提出多項條件後，終在會議尾聲作出承諾，表示將會轉交專頁擁有人身份予WhatsNews總編輯Meow，並在5人同意下一同簽定協議落實。<br />\n<br />\n時至今日本該是主權移交之時，奈何Jerry Lo並沒有履行當日承諾。為了WhatsNews日後仍然能夠繼續營運，為大眾捍衛真理報道真相，WhatsNews總編輯Meow、攝影記者Luci、前線記者里奧、K將會重新建立WhatsNews Facebook專頁。<br />\n<br />\n而Jerry Lo違反合約精神的行為以及為WhatsNews帶來的一切損失，我們將保留追究權利，特此聲明及敬告各位讀者。<br />\n<br />\nTg:<a href=\"https://t.me/WhatsNewsHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWhatsNewsHK&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=0330cfd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WhatsNewsHK</a>"},{"pid":"7b39d08e16f40c85946a189bdd0c5568e0ed1bbf","tid":2205285,"uid":16135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:48:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f71b899e53cba9b6b39972a8e454d7dfb936735","tid":2205285,"uid":16135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dd3d41741a0e11e363b8f6e4367f5b5dd0d7be0","tid":2205285,"uid":16135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de07b21a0fb14433859faa3eded40e048163076","tid":2205285,"uid":56274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020